Actress Amber Heard has become one of the most hated after she was accused of defamation along with The Sun newspaper by her ex-husband Johnny Depp because during the nefarious trial some unfavorable details of the actress were revealed. But, compared to her ex-partner, the actress seems to continue her career without any dilemma and, according to a report, Amber Heard could join Star Wars in an upcoming project.
